1092
01:50:24,088 --> 01:50:26,429
[SPEAKER_19]: We've been talking about public safety, the police department.

1093
01:50:26,709 --> 01:50:28,710
[SPEAKER_19]: We've been talking about the need for additional cruises.

1094
01:50:28,970 --> 01:50:39,253
