01:50:39,853 --> 01:50:44,875
[SPEAKER_19]: And really, every year, we never really address those particular issues in the budget.

1096
01:50:45,275 --> 01:50:50,017
[SPEAKER_19]: It's more or less just looking at last year's budget and adding or decreasing lines.

